description:
She is part of a family of policewomen found in almost every town. All of her sisters are named the same, and look identical. They are responsible for enforcing the law, and are often called on when Team Rocket is causing trouble. They typically use Growlithe as an attacking Pokemon. They are also part of Brock`s innumerable fantasies about girls, and he seems to be the only one able to tell the various officers apart.
The Officer Jennys that are apart of the Orange Islands Police Force have lighter uniforms than those of the Kanto Region.
name: Junsaa
